<td style="text-align: center; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: #ffffff;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 14px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;"><strong>This letter is to inform you of certain cybersecurity requirements effective November 30, 2020 that require Honeywell suppliers in the US Government supply chain to take necessary steps in ensuring compliance prior to receiving further orders after November 30, 2020</strong>.</span><br></td> 
